1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,620
=Episode 21=
(Obedience)

3
00:01:28,200 --> 00:01:28,959
Don't just stand there!

4
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,079
Get cleaning now!

5
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:32,000
Mom.

6
00:01:33,719 --> 00:01:34,799
For the past five years,

7
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,840
you haven't changed one bit.

8
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,680
Don't act high and mighty with me.

9
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,599
As long as you are here,

10
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:42,280
you are our daughter-in-law.

11
00:01:43,439 --> 00:01:44,400
Qingmei,

12
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:48,040
you don't want everyone to know

13
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,920
about your secrets with Jinchuan,
do you?

14
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:52,799
I heard

15
00:01:54,079 --> 00:01:55,200
you only got into Mu Shaoze's bed

16
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:56,879
by scheming.

17
00:01:58,319 --> 00:02:00,120
How are you any better than me?

18
00:02:02,439 --> 00:02:02,920
You...

19
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,239
Shut your mouth!

20
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,159
So hot!

21
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:11,000
Jinxi!

22
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:11,759
So hot!

23
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:12,639
Are you okay?

24
00:02:12,639 --> 00:02:13,479
So hot!

25
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,439
Jinxi!

26
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,120
Why are you doing this to me?

27
00:02:16,479 --> 00:02:17,599
I know you don't like me.

28
00:02:17,719 --> 00:02:18,800
You don't want me back.

29
00:02:19,319 --> 00:02:21,400
But this is still my home!

30
00:02:22,439 --> 00:02:23,360
What?

31
00:02:23,639 --> 00:02:25,000
Stop pretending, you witch!

32
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:25,599
Jinxi!

33
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,199
What are you doing?

34
00:02:29,639 --> 00:02:30,120
Dad!

35
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,479
She... she burned me!

36
00:02:31,879 --> 00:02:32,919
How many times have I told you?

37
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,520
Qingmei is your sister-in-law.

38
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:36,639
Don't bully her just because she's kind!

39
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,240
Look at what she did to Jinxi's leg!

40
00:02:38,439 --> 00:02:39,319
And you...

41
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:40,159
Look!

42
00:02:40,319 --> 00:02:41,840
Look how you've spoiled her!

43
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,120
They're all useless

44
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,360
and rude!

45
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:49,759
Qingmei.

46
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,039
Dad.

47
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:53,639
I'll stand up for you.

48
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,960
Whoever dares to bully you,

49
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,400
I'll throw them out.

50
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,400
Thank you, Dad.

51
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,159
He Mingyuan!

52
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:15,719
You got me.

53
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,120
He Mingyuan!

54
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:34,039
Where's your conscience?

55
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:36,319
I gave you two sons and a daughter!

56
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,919
And now everything is my fault?

57
00:03:37,919 --> 00:03:39,719
All you ever do is yell!

58
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,800
Aren't you supposed to be
recovering at the villa?

59
00:03:42,039 --> 00:03:42,879
Why do you come back?

60
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,199
If I hadn't come back,

61
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:46,360
you'd have kicked Jinchuan away.

62
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:47,280
Are you planning

63
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:48,960
to kick Jinxi away too?

64
00:03:49,159 --> 00:03:51,439
Jinchuan brought it upon himself.

65
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:52,960
A useless son,

66
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,439
I'd rather not have him at all.

67
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,719
You have the nerve to criticize my son?

68
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,240
I know

69
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,800
about your dirty secret so well.

70
00:04:01,639 --> 00:04:03,879
You've been obsessed with your
first love's daughter for years!

71
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,159
You're sick!

72
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:06,680
Shut up!

73
00:04:06,879 --> 00:04:07,360
Mom!

74
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,240
Someone!

75
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,199
Dad!

76
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,280
Why did you push mom?

77
00:04:12,439 --> 00:04:13,719
Get this crazy woman out of here!

78
00:04:13,919 --> 00:04:14,639
Lock her up!

79
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,160
She's not to see anyone!

80
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:17,279
You're a pervert!

81
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:18,000
Get her out!

82
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,720
Pervert!

83
00:04:18,879 --> 00:04:19,040
You...

84
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:19,759
Jinxi!

85
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:22,240
You're not allowed to see
this crazy woman again!

86
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:22,879
Otherwise,

87
00:04:22,959 --> 00:04:24,519
move out of here before the engagement!

88
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:29,600
Do you hear me?

89
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:35,920
Get out!

90
00:04:41,519 --> 00:04:42,600
I only got part of the recording

91
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,079
from He Jinxi.

92
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,079
For the rest,

93
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:47,519
she's hidden them well.

94
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,360
And now He Jinchuan has gone missing.

95
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,600
All we can do now is
dig deeper into Meiyan.

96
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:55,519
I've already spoken to Niannian.

97
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:57,680
If there's any news of He Jinchuan,

98
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,040
she'll notify me right away.

99
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:05,199
We've planted an asset

100
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,360
inside Meiyan International.

101
00:05:07,519 --> 00:05:09,800
It's just a matter of time
before they make a move.

102
00:05:10,319 --> 00:05:12,639
So we need to
get the key evidence quickly.

103
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:14,759
Now that He Jinchen

104
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:16,319
has already got the resort,

105
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:19,079
the entire He Group will be the next.

106
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,720
He Jinchen is too greedy.

107
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:27,000
He wants to take Gu Corporation
from Gu Qingmei

108
00:05:27,759 --> 00:05:29,199
and even make you his wife.

109
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,800
I think he's actually fallen for you.

110
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,439
He puts profit above everything.

111
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:35,319
How could he truly love me?

112
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:39,279
You don't get it.

113
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,439
The harder something is to get,

114
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:42,959
the more they want it.

115
00:05:47,519 --> 00:05:48,720
I sense some jealousy.

116
00:05:48,959 --> 00:05:51,000
Where does it come from?

117
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:01,040
You look pale.

118
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,120
Are you sick?

119
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,040
I'm fine.

120
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:07,360
Let's go to the hospital.

121
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,319
No,

122
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,480
it's just my period.

123
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:16,600
What should I do?

124
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,680
Put me down, then I'll tell you.

125
00:06:20,079 --> 00:06:20,519
Alright.

126
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,160
You're pulling my hair.

127
00:06:45,959 --> 00:06:47,519
A warm boba tea always helps

128
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,279
when the pain hits.

129
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,480
Why did you buy all this stuff?

130
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:59,000
I passed by the convenience store
and grabbed a few things.

131
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:00,560
Want some candy?

132
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,319
Why did you buy candy?

133
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,079
So I'm a kid now?

134
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:08,759
The clerk said

135
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:11,319
when you're in pain, a piece of candy

136
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:12,920
can help.

137
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:17,279
You don't like it?

138
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,360
Alright.

139
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,560
Whenever I was in severe pain before,

140
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:27,519
my dad would buy me boba tea,

141
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,600
and my mom would rub my stomach.

142
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:37,839
Rub... not pinch.

143
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,160
Thank you

144
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,839
for giving me that feeling of
having my parents again.

145
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:48,600
Now, this is your boyfriend.

146
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,759
Alright, boyfriend.

147
00:08:01,279 --> 00:08:01,879
Who is it?

148
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,240
You again?

149
00:08:09,759 --> 00:08:10,240
Where's Su Li?

150
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,199
Move.

151
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,000
Su Li!

152
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,199
Su Li!

153
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,120
Why are you here?

154
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:19,199
I need some time.

155
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,879
I can make you Mrs. He,

156
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:22,519
and

157
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:24,920
I can help you take back Gu Corporation.

158
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:27,120
Don't you get it?

159
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,279
That's not what I want at all.

160
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,399
Su Li!

161
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,159
He Jinchen,

162
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:34,679
your wife is at home.

163
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,559
Can you stop claiming
people who aren't yours?

164
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,279
Mu Shaoze,

165
00:08:39,879 --> 00:08:41,320
your fiancée is at home.

166
00:08:41,639 --> 00:08:42,799
What are you doing here?

167
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:43,720
What are you?

168
00:08:43,879 --> 00:08:44,279
What are you?

169
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:44,919
Enough!

170
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:46,399
Both of you, leave!

171
00:08:47,039 --> 00:08:48,039
Go back to your own homes

172
00:08:48,159 --> 00:08:49,000
and your own women.

173
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,360
Go!

174
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,000
I... I...

175
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,159
Go! Go!

176
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,159
- Su Li!
- Su Li!

177
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,200
You...

178
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:56,879
- Move!
- Move!

179
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:57,519
What are you doing?

180
00:08:59,240 --> 00:08:59,720
Su Li!

181
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,600
- Get lost!
- Su Li!

182
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:02,799
No peace at all.

183
00:09:28,519 --> 00:09:29,120
Mingyuan,

184
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,799
you're really good at chess.

185
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:34,320
I lost.

186
00:09:47,759 --> 00:09:48,600
You know,

187
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:52,840
I met your mother at a chess club.

188
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:57,559
She was far better than me.

189
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,399
No matter how hard I tried,
I could never beat her.

190
00:10:01,399 --> 00:10:03,360
In the end, I'd still lose.

191
00:10:06,039 --> 00:10:07,559
I've lost my whole life.

192
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,120
How about

193
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,519
another round of chess?

194
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:19,720
Forget it.

195
00:10:22,840 --> 00:10:23,679
You do look like her,

196
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,080
but you're not her.

197
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,360
Don't worry,

198
00:10:34,279 --> 00:10:35,799
I won't do anything to you.

199
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:38,120
I just want you to stay with me.

200
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:12,519
Mr. Lin,

201
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,039
this is your sister, right?

202
00:11:15,639 --> 00:11:17,200
She used Meiyan's skincare products,

203
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:18,919
developed skin cancer,
and committed suicide.

204
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:20,240
That skincare set,

205
00:11:20,360 --> 00:11:21,639
you gave it to her as a birthday gift.

206
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:22,919
Why?

207
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:25,120
Why would you poison your own sister?

208
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:26,840
No, I didn't do that.

209
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,639
I was new to the company.

210
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,120
I was just a regular employee.

211
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,360
Only after I got promoted

212
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,759
that I found out they'd been using

213
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,919
a prohibited ingredient called TAF990.

214
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:38,200
In the short term,

215
00:11:38,639 --> 00:11:40,159
it makes your skin glow.

216
00:11:40,879 --> 00:11:41,840
But long-term use

217
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,159
carries a high cancer risk.

218
00:11:45,279 --> 00:11:45,919
Mr. Lin,

219
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:48,519
are you still going to take his side?

220
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:51,320
More girls would suffer
just like your sister!

221
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:56,440
Still not talking?

222
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:58,799
You know very well

223
00:11:59,919 --> 00:12:01,039
what He Jinchen is capable of.

224
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,519
Once you're no longer useful to him,

225
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:04,799
do you think

226
00:12:05,600 --> 00:12:07,080
he'll let you walk away clean?

227
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,759
Alright.

228
00:12:14,080 --> 00:12:14,799
I'll help you.

229
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,780
(He Jinchuan)

230
00:12:20,780 --> 00:12:23,300
(Recording)

231
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:31,960
Hello.

232
00:12:32,519 --> 00:12:32,960
Mr. Mu.

233
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,440
I'd like to meet you tonight.

234
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,159
Sure.

235
00:12:38,240 --> 00:12:39,120
Let's talk in person.

236
00:12:46,039 --> 00:12:46,840
Why is he not showing up?

237
00:12:49,279 --> 00:12:49,840
Miss Su.

238
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:54,799
Although He Jinchen fired me openly,

239
00:12:55,200 --> 00:12:55,799
I am

240
00:12:55,960 --> 00:12:57,320
still taking care of some things.

241
00:12:58,639 --> 00:13:00,279
That makes it easier
for us to investigate.

242
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:02,799
Any new findings?

243
00:13:03,279 --> 00:13:06,360
I found the TAF990 ingredient files

244
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:08,960
in his office safe.

245
00:13:09,679 --> 00:13:11,519
But I don't know the combination.

246
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:12,679
Maybe

247
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:15,159
we can get his spare key instead.

248
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:16,879
His key?

249
00:13:28,919 --> 00:13:31,159
I think I've seen it.

250
00:13:31,879 --> 00:13:33,080
He always keeps it on him.

251
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,879
I'll go back

252
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,360
and try to get the key.

253
00:13:36,519 --> 00:13:36,960
No.

254
00:13:37,799 --> 00:13:38,879
It's too dangerous now.

255
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,080
Sis.

256
00:13:50,039 --> 00:13:50,799
Why are you here?

257
00:13:51,559 --> 00:13:53,679
We agreed to stick to the plan.

258
00:13:55,519 --> 00:13:56,639
There's been a change.

259
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,600
Did they bully you again?

260
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,000
What brings you here today?

261
00:14:04,639 --> 00:14:06,279
I need to borrow your identity

262
00:14:06,399 --> 00:14:06,960
for something.

263
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,159
Fish soup again?

264
00:14:19,679 --> 00:14:21,519
You can't even get
the family's diet right.

265
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,960
How can you take over Gu Corporation?

266
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,039
You...

267
00:14:31,639 --> 00:14:32,240
You are...

268
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:36,240
Dad.

269
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,559
Dad.

270
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,480
Where's Mom?

271
00:14:44,600 --> 00:14:45,519
She's not coming for dinner again?

272
00:14:47,559 --> 00:14:48,720
She's not feeling well,

273
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:50,480
so she's staying in her room.

274
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:53,279
Dear,

275
00:14:54,120 --> 00:14:54,639
try some soup.

276
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:55,559
Dad,

277
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:56,960
I lost my appetite.

278
00:14:57,559 --> 00:14:58,240
Don't mind me.

279
00:15:35,260 --> 00:15:40,020
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

280
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:44,860
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

281
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:49,420
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

282
00:15:49,420 --> 00:15:54,340
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

283
00:15:54,340 --> 00:15:58,140
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

284
00:15:58,140 --> 00:16:02,940
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

285
00:16:02,940 --> 00:16:05,780
♪Can't remember
when this flutter started♪

286
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:08,460
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

287
00:16:08,820 --> 00:16:14,380
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

288
00:16:14,780 --> 00:16:21,580
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

289
00:16:21,860 --> 00:16:26,540
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

290
